muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.poster.avif?t=1667248141\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.webm?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.mp4?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/a7e32e50c96586187440d5005f9e8711.avif?t=1667248141\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>While playing you can either focus on surviving for as long as possible or to top your own highscore.<br>Whereas time constantly ticks up, your score depends on how quickly you can dispatch enemies as well as your method.<br>Playing in a stylish way will reward you with more points to be added to your score.",
